#=iCloud==============================================================================
IMAPAccount fastmail
Host imap.fastmail.com
User inbox@djmcdowell.com
PassCmd "gpg -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d $XDG_DATA_HOME/.mbsyncpass.gpg"
Port 993
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2
AuthMechs Login

IMAPStore fastmail-remote
Account fastmail

MaildirStore fastmail-local
Path ~/Mail/
Inbox ~/Mail/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

#
# Channels and Groups
# (so that we can rename local directories and flatten the hierarchy)
#
#
Channel fastmail
Master :fastmail-remote:
Slave :fastmail-local:
Patterns *
Create Slave
Sync All
Expunge Both
CopyArrivalDate yes
SyncState *
